\newcommand*{\simtechcontent}{\lentry{%
My responsibility was running fluid interaction and heat transfer simulations, analysing the results and finally giving reports on the simulations to different customers (mostly foundries). The main tools I used was Flow3D (CFD software) and Solidworks (CAD modelling software). I have also held training sessions for numerous Finnish and international customers.%
